    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So Prototype.js (< 1.7.2) actually replaces the `bind` method in every cases: https://github.com/sstephenson/prototype/commit/9559d8892d9edb8bdf53391c11dfa32bdaf6bf39\n",
